Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.50,0:00:58.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看它们翻滚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:00:58.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See them flip
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.92,0:01:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看它们翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See them soar
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.70,0:01:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看它们杂耍  还有更多花样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,see them juggle and so much more
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.20,0:01:07.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是海跳蚤马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:07.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Circus Sea Fleas
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.22,0:01:12.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们生来就要让你快快乐乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:12.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And they were born to please you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.75,0:01:18.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们爱你  海跳蚤马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:18.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We love you, Circus Sea Fleas
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.01,0:01:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳蚤们也爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the fleas love you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.50,0:01:25.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记住  海跳蚤马戏团生来只为你演出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:25.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, Circus Sea Fleas live to perform just for you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.21,0:01:28.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们打心里十分认可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:28.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been emotionally validated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:29.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1020,514)}海跳蚤马戏团
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.21,0:01:31.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上订购你专属的海跳蚤马戏团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:31.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Send for your very own Circus Sea Fleas today
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:30.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1520,546)}马上订购
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.07,0:01:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我昨天就订了  还在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sent for mine yesterday, and I'm still waiting
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.33,0:01:38.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真倒霉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:38.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bummer, dude
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.57,0:01:39.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:39.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:40.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1036,232)}真倒霉啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.38,0:01:41.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒霉哥手办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:41.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bummer Dude action figures
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.50,0:01:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痛苦无比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're miserable
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,316)}倒霉哥手办
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.29,0:01:46.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:46.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.66,0:01:49.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天有一堆好东西要给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:49.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got a buncha great stuff for you today
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1604,872)}邮件
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.88,0:01:52.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全新一册锅铲商城目录
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:52.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The new "Spatula Emporium" catalog
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:52.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(442,252)}锅铲
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.14,0:01:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是这
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.22,0:01:57.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你中彩得到的奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:57.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free money from the sweepstakes you won
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1394,262)}海绵宝宝\N一百万
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.66,0:01:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是这
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:01:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.75,0:02:01.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你家里人寄来的信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:01.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A letter from your family
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.72,0:02:06.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是这
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:06.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.47,0:02:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,包裹  有没有包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Packages, how about packages?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.37,0:02:09.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有寄给我的包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:09.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have any packages for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.82,0:02:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.82,0:02:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No packages
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.75,0:02:13.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你失望了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:13.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.39,0:02:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你从哪看出来我失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What makes you think I'm disappointed?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.47,0:02:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything's just fine
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好难过的海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man, what a sad sponge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(988,288)}难过海绵
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  隆重推出难过海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, introducing Sad Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.79,0:02:30.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最新款倒霉哥手办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:30.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The newest Bummer Dude action figure
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踢一踢  扭一扭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And kick, and twist
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.70,0:02:35.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踢一踢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:35.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and kick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踢高一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Higher ladies
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.95,0:02:38.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说高一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:38.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said higher
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.90,0:02:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你见识什么叫高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you high
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.29,0:02:56.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感受燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:56.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feel the burn
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.30,0:03:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉红色的护腿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pink leg warmers?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可是护腿兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're leg warmer buddies
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, please
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.52,0:03:23.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不会戴着那顶帽子穿护腿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:23.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be caught dead in leg warmers with that hat
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回时装学校补补课去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go back to fashion school
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  时装学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, fashion school?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要回去补课
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming back
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.25,0:03:37.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我重生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:37.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm reborn
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.00,0:03:39.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:39.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这包裹不是寄给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This package isn't even for me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(760,726)}裤头村 贝壳街{\fnArial}124{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}号\N海绵宝宝收
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是寄给海绵宝宝的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's for SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.07,0:03:50.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那邮递员简直笨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:50.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That mailman is a moron
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃东西时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And time for me to eat
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.62,0:04:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碗干干净净
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bowl is nice and clean
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿起小勺子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grab my favorite spoon
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿衬衣擦一擦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Polish it on my shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(370,902)}牛奶
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.00,0:04:22.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牛奶味道鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:22.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Milk is smelling fresh
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麦片促活力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cereal gives me pep
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:30.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550,500)}海草麦片圈
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它自己在动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's moving by itself
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碗里闹鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts are in my bowl
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碗里闹鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts are in my bowl?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碗里闹鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts are in my bowl
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我厨房闹鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My kitchen's haunted
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.52,0:05:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.25,0:05:23.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你太累了  所以才会出幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just seeing things because you're so tired
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多睡一会就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just need some more sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.76,0:05:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1244,582)}海跳蚤马戏团
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我肯定还在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must still be dreaming
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.91,0:06:20.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临你的海跳蚤马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:20.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to your Sea Flea Circus
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.31,0:06:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为你提供娱乐是我们的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's our duty to entertain you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How delightful
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.85,0:06:44.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:44.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's next?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,午餐时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lunchtime
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,午餐时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lunchtime?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.78,0:06:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做个梦还吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would a dream need a--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't a dream
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是家里闹跳蚤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an infestation
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.47,0:07:37.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳蚤哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:37.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.45,0:07:41.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:41.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我样子好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I look amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.65,0:07:54.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别咬我脸  把我美貌给毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:54.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't ruin this by biting my face
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们毁了我美貌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ruined it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(856,632)}面粉
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.07,0:08:15.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么我会遭这种罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:15.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.90,0:08:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.40,0:08:21.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是报应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:21.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karma
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.24,0:08:23.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.49,0:08:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.47,0:08:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That feels nice and warm
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(790,436)}烘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1262,492)}焦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1114,922)}脆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(690,848)}煨
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.09,0:08:38.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在有点热了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:38.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's actually getting kind of hot now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.20,0:08:42.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这是要把我烤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:42.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're trying to cook me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.22,0:08:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欧洲萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Parsnip?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.94,0:08:57.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这种上等肉可不能配欧洲萝卜吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:53.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't serve
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:57.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a prime piece of meat like me with parsnip
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.09,0:09:00.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要加柠檬提味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:09:00.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need lemons to brighten my flavors
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.90,0:09:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要加胡椒或者香料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and some pepper or spice
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Much better
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let me out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.49,0:09:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样做就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you're cookin'
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.56,0:09:33.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  我纽扣脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:33.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, my buttons are tarnished
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马戏团跳蚤肯定不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No circus flea is going to want
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在纽扣脏的人面前表演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to perform for a guy with tarnished buttons
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马戏团音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Circus music?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just checking
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.55,0:10:03.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有没有看到过个寄给我的包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:03.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've haven't seen a package addressed to me, have you?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的马戏团跳蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My circus fleas
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,寄过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They came
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,寄过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They came
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盒子是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This box is empty
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.75,0:10:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳蚤哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did the fleas go?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳蚤们好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, fleas
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你帮忙喂过跳蚤了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope you fed them, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们会饿得慌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They can get pretty hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.13,0:10:26.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经喂过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:26.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I fed them all right
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.97,0:10:28.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧取走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:28.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please take them away now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.61,0:10:49.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把马戏团带到我家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:49.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's take this circus to my place
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体上车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All aboard
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.50,0:11:02.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愿你每一天都能拥有海跳蚤马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May all your days be Sea Flea Circus days
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.27,0:11:05.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:05.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.90,0:11:12.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨蛋马戏团跳蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:12.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stupid circus fleas
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.32,0:11:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看留下的这么一堆烂摊子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at the mess they left
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.68,0:11:16.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:16.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
