Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:40.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(630,396)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.87,0:11:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干什么要那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's taking so long?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.72,0:11:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我薯条都吃不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never got my fries
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么我爸不爱我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't my father love me?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.32,0:11:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.40,0:11:54.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:54.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.77,0:11:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.75,0:11:56.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:56.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.09,0:11:56.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:56.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生  清理卫生间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward, clean up in the head
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.87,0:12:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有清理这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Also, clean up here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.96,0:12:08.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:08.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说赶快清理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said clean up
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.49,0:12:11.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:11.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.05,0:12:11.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:11.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.92,0:12:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别光躺在那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't just lay there
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.60,0:12:27.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去清理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:27.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clean up
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚只是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was just a dream
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.12,0:12:40.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怕又真实无比的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:40.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a horrible, realistic, totally on point dream
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.55,0:12:43.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我居然会梦见我在上班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:43.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm dreaming about work
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.67,0:12:47.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明明还有不少有意思的事情可以做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when there's so many more
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:47.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,interesting things I could be doing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.26,0:12:49.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看我没画完的画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:49.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at my unfinished painting
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没作完的交响曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And my unfinished symphony
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有没吃的薄酥卷饼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And my uneaten strudel
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.04,0:12:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的薄酥卷饼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My strudel
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,味道跟普通馅饼一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just tasted like pie to me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.92,0:13:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是薄酥卷饼  你个野蛮人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a strudel, you barbarian
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看上面油酥面皮这么多层
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at those pastry layers
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.97,0:13:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.03,0:13:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才刚醒来  一整天就已经乱套了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just woke up and the day's already a disaster
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天完全无法面对蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't face the Krusty Krab today
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.25,0:13:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要待家里  潜入章鱼哥的美丽海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am staying home and diving into an ocean of Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(596,630)}夹心糖
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.82,0:13:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种多层馅饼还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any more of that layer pie?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.92,0:13:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来除掉我身上另外的重担
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now to get rid of the other monkey on my back
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, it's
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.70,0:14:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.72,0:14:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在电话那头干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing on the phone?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.95,0:14:12.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该在上班的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:12.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should be working
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.47,0:14:15.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:15.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't work
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.88,0:14:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.20,0:14:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,病重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你声音听起来还挺不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do sound pretty bad
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定你病重得上不了班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're too sick to work?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.03,0:14:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.58,0:14:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,positive
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.51,0:14:35.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,病重是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:35.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too sick, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有办法可以治好你的病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got the cure for what ails you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.17,0:14:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好休息  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you just rest up, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.20,0:14:44.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有事情我都会照顾好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:44.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of everything
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, bye
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.25,0:14:45.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回头再说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:45.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,talk to you--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.62,0:14:46.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:46.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, I mean--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人能在蟹老板面前装病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one fake sick on Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.09,0:14:53.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还蒙混过关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:53.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and gets away with it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.09,0:14:57.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天我不用上班
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:57.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No work for me today
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生放心玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward gets to play
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没客人可以恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No customers for me to fear
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.67,0:15:06.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝能沿着尖码头一路走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:06.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob can take a long walk along a very sharp pier
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是我点的蔬菜拼盘到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That must be the crudité I ordered
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.03,0:15:11.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:11.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没看到你在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't see you there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.09,0:15:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好贴心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.09,0:15:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How thoughtful of you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.62,0:15:24.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能在我身体虚的时候来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:24.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to visit me in my weakened state
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别放在心上  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think nothing of it, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你打电话声音感觉特别不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sounded so bad on the phone
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.54,0:15:30.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就赶过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:30.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I rushed right over
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.94,0:15:33.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确保你把自己照顾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:33.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make sure you were taking good care of yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.85,0:15:36.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不能把别人传染了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:36.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I wouldn't want to infect anyone
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你或许应该得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you should probably go now
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.45,0:15:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在可不适合自己一个人待家里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are in no condition to be alone
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.32,0:15:45.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我才给你带了帮手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:45.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's why I brought you some help
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让这位来治你  早上打电话找我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take one of these and call me in the morning
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,医生来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The doctor is in
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用襁褓裹住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Swaddle, swaddle, swaddle
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.57,0:15:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静  别把自己拉伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hush-aby now, don't strain yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.66,0:16:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说真的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.80,0:16:04.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这没多大必要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:04.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this isn't necessary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然有必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course it is
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.30,0:16:10.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是让我发现你是在装病翘班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I find out you were faking it just to get out of work
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.38,0:16:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只能开除你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd have to fire you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没装病
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No faking here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没  我真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm really--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.22,0:16:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,病了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  继续裹襁褓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, back to the swaddling
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.61,0:16:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.77,0:16:33.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:33.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.72,0:16:35.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:35.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.54,0:16:38.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:38.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你劳累过度了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're overexerting yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快让你身患重病的小小身体好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you just rest that sick little body of yours
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.17,0:16:46.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我海绵宝宝来帮你画完你的自画像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while SpongeBob finishes up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your self-portrait for you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.06,0:16:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.18,0:16:51.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:51.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Done
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我的想象中  你是个无助的小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In my imagination, you're a helpless little baby
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.40,0:16:57.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你病情比我想的还要重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:57.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're sicker than I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把那个黄色讨厌鬼忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now just forget that yellow nuisance
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让自己沉浸在音乐当中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and lose yourself in music
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.32,0:17:17.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你身体这么虚  可不能浪费口气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be wasting your breath
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:17.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in your weakened state
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.27,0:17:19.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮你吹竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:19.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me blow the clarinet for you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.45,0:17:21.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不  别碰我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:21.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, don't touch my--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.87,0:17:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别碰我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't touch my--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.27,0:17:46.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美的薄酥卷饼会让一切顺顺利利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:46.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The perfect strudel will make everything all right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.54,0:17:47.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该来测体温了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to take your temperature
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.21,0:17:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快把那东西给我拿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get that thing away from my--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(956,920)}{\fnArial}37{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}摄氏度
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.27,0:17:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,98.6度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,98.6
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你已经好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Squidward, you're all better
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.12,0:18:04.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好高兴我们俩都能回蟹堡王去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:04.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy we can both go to the Krusty Krab now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.18,0:18:04.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:04.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.05,0:18:06.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把那东西给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:06.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that thing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定是读数读错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must've read it wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.76,0:18:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that over there?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.90,0:18:11.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:11.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一堵墙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A wall
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.18,0:18:16.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好顺滑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:16.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So smooth
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.07,0:18:20.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚才真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:20.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that was fun
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.97,0:18:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来读一下体温计吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's check that thermometer again, shall we?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.07,0:18:24.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:24.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.38,0:18:28.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高烧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:28.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A fever
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.28,0:18:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  必须把你冷却下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, we got to cool you off
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.67,0:18:34.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:34.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对  还得更冷点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, you need it even colder
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.87,0:18:49.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:49.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  舒服点没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, all better?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没  你个傻蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,N-no, you buffoon
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.72,0:18:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.97,0:18:57.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:57.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have been
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.26,0:18:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,犯傻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,buffoon
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,W-w-what?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.20,0:19:03.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我之前一直都是治标不治本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:02.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been treating the symptoms
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:03.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,instead of the sickness
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.49,0:19:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别拿那东西靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay away from me with that thing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是必须要知道你得的是什么病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we have to figure out what you have
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才能治
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so we can treat it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.46,0:19:09.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:09.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经知道我得的是什么病了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I already know what I have
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.14,0:19:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,急性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,acute
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.94,0:19:14.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疱疹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:14.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,spotting
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斯克罗博病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sclorboritis
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.26,0:19:19.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,急性疱疹斯克罗博病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:19.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Acute spotting sclorboritis?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.66,0:19:21.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没听过那种病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:21.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never heard of that one
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.70,0:19:22.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:22.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better look it up
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.17,0:19:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,病情恶化了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're getting worse
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要赶快找到治疗方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to find a cure fast
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.62,0:19:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it is
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.47,0:19:35.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,治疗方法好像还挺简单
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the cure seems pretty simple
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(968,292)}急性疱疹斯克罗博病
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.47,0:19:38.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:38.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.06,0:19:40.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:40.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.32,0:19:42.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  我有说急性斑点斯克罗博病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:42.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wait, did I say acute spotting sclorboritis?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我肯定想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, I must've meant
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,普勒金顿综合征
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,plerkington's syndrome
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.80,0:19:49.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:49.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Found it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来开始治疗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get to the curing, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:52.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,288)}普勒金顿综合征
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,治好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are we done?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.32,0:20:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've just begun
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.40,0:20:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tentacle's residence
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob speaking
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.51,0:20:31.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  我的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:31.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, me boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.85,0:20:32.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,病人怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:32.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's the patient?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.82,0:20:34.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:34.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.72,0:20:35.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:35.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm all better
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.94,0:20:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  让我回去上班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, just let me go back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nonsense
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看着还是病得不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You still look so sick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加大治疗力度  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better step up the cure, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就听你的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘴巴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open wide
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.25,0:21:00.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你休想让那东西靠近我嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:21:00.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will not get that anywhere near my mouth
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.15,0:21:02.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:02.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(654,434)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是根据书上的指示  我撑大他鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, the book told me to stretch his nose
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.70,0:21:10.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用水母电他  然后把他肺部刮了一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:10.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,shock him with a jellyfish, and then I scraped his lungs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再用一只食毒海胆把脏东西都清了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and cleaned them out with a toxic eating urchin
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Priceless
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.11,0:21:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.64,0:21:25.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生病几天过后感觉好点没
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:25.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feeling better after your sick day?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.01,0:21:27.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所言极是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:27.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You might say that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.69,0:21:35.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:35.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's glorious
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.54,0:21:38.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  我从前有厌烦一切的毛病
